             was indicted for <rs id="t18260112-37-off218" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18260112-37-off218" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260112-37-off218" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18260112-37-cd219" type="crimeDate">23d of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260112-37-off218 t18260112-37-cd219"></join>, 70lbs. weight of iron, value 5s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18260112-37-victim310" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Allen
                     <interp inst="t18260112-37-victim310" type="surname" value="Allen"></interp>
